songs.title: Parking lot
songs.lyrics:
[Verse] x2
I had a panic attack in your dorm room
And all you did was tell me to grow up
Because i trusted you with my adolescent thoughts
Now i'm alone in this parking lot

I had a panic attack in your dorm room
And all you did was tell me to grow up
Because i trusted you with my adolescent thoughts
